msgstr "ໂຫຼດໂຄງສ້າງໂຄງການຄືນໃໝ່"

#: kiledocmanager.cpp:1287
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The current document is not associated to a project. Please activate a "
"document that is associated to the project you want to build the tree for, "
"then choose Refresh Project Tree again."
msgstr ""
"ເອກະສານປັດຈຸບັນບໍ່ໄດ້ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງກັບໂຄງການໃດເລີຍ. "
"ກະລຸນາເປີດໃຊ້ເອກະສານທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງກັບໂຄງການທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການສ້າງໂຄງສ້າງ, "
"ແລ້ວເລືອກ ໂຫຼດໂຄງສ້າງໂຄງການຄືນໃໝ່ ອີກຄັ້ງ."

#: kiledocmanager.cpp:1287
#, kde-format
msgid "Could Not Refresh Project Tree"
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດໂຫຼດໂຄງສ້າງໂຄງການຄືນໃໝ່ໄດ້"

#: kiledocmanager.cpp:1371 kiledocmanager.cpp:2130 kiledocmanager.cpp:2200
#: kiledocmanager.cpp:2235
#, kde-format
msgid "Select Project"
msgstr "ເລືອກໂຄງການ"

#: kiledocmanager.cpp:1396 kiledocmanager.cpp:1411 kiledocmanager.cpp:1418
#, kde-format
msgid "Add to Project"
msgstr "ເພີ່ມໃສ່ໂຄງການ"

#: kiledocmanager.cpp:1410
#, kde-format
msgid "The file %1 is already member of the project %2"
msgstr "ໄຟລ໌ %1 ເປັນສະມາຊິກຂອງໂຄງການ %2 ຢູ່ແລ້ວ"

#: kiledocmanager.cpp:1417
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The file %1 can not be added because it does not exist or is not readable"
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດເພີ່ມໄຟລ໌ %1 ໄດ້ ເພາະມັນບໍ່ມີຢູ່ ຫຼື ບໍ່ສາມາດອ່ານໄດ້"

#: kiledocmanager.cpp:1436
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This file is the project file, which holds all the information about your "
"project.  As such, it cannot be removed from the project."
msgstr ""
"ໄຟລ໌ນີ້ແມ່ນໄຟລ໌ໂຄງການ, ເຊິ່ງເກັບຂໍ້ມູນທັງໝົດກ່ຽວກັບໂຄງການຂອງທ່ານ. ດັ່ງນັ້ນ, "
"ມັນບໍ່ສາມາດຖືກລຶບອອກຈາກໂຄງການໄດ້."

#: kiledocmanager.cpp:1436
#, kde-format
msgid "Cannot Remove File From Project"
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດລຶບໄຟລ໌ອອກຈາກໂຄງການໄດ້"

#: kiledocmanager.cpp:1504
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>The project \"%1\" is already open.</p><p>If you wanted to reload the "
"project, close the project before you re-open it.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>ໂຄງການ \"%1\" ເປີດຢູ່ແລ້ວ.</p><p>ຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການໂຫຼດໂຄງການຄືນໃໝ່, "
"ໃຫ້ປິດໂຄງການກ່ອນທີ່ທ່ານຈະເປີດມັນຄືນໃໝ່.</p>"

#: kiledocmanager.cpp:1506
#, kde-format
msgid "Project Already Open"
msgstr "ໂຄງການເປີດຢູ່ແລ້ວ"

#: kiledocmanager.cpp:1517
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>The project file for the project \"%1\" does not exist or it is not "
"readable.</p><p>Do you want to remove this project from the recent projects "
"list?</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>ໄຟລ໌ໂຄງການສຳລັບໂຄງການ \"%1\" ບໍ່ມີຢູ່ ຫຼື ບໍ່ສາມາດອ່ານໄດ້.</"
"p><p>ທ່ານຕ້ອງການລຶບໂຄງການນີ້ອອກຈາກລາຍການໂຄງການຫຼ້າສຸດຫຼືບໍ່?</p>"

#: kiledocmanager.cpp:1520
#, kde-format
msgid "Could Not Open Project"
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດເປີດໂຄງການໄດ້"

#: kiledocmanager.cpp:1538
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>The file \"%1\" cannot be opened as it does not appear to be a project "
"file.</p>"
msgstr "<p>ບໍ່ສາມາດເປີດໄຟລ໌ \"%1\" ໄດ້ ເນື່ອງຈາກມັນບໍ່ແມ່ນໄຟລ໌ໂຄງການ.</p>"

#: kiledocmanager.cpp:1540
#, kde-format
msgid "Impossible to Open Project File"
msgstr "ເປັນໄປບໍ່ໄດ້ທີ່ຈະເປີດໄຟລ໌ໂຄງການ"

#: kiledocmanager.cpp:1550
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>The project \"%1\" cannot be opened as it was created <br/>by a newer "
"version of Kile.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>ບໍ່ສາມາດເປີດໂຄງການ \"%1\" ໄດ້ ເນື່ອງຈາກມັນຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນ <br/>ໂດຍ Kile "
"ເວີຊັນໃໝ່ກວ່າ.</p>"

#: kiledocmanager.cpp:1552
#, kde-format
msgid "Impossible to Open Project"
msgstr "ເປັນໄປບໍ່ໄດ້ທີ່ຈະເປີດໂຄງການ"

#: kiledocmanager.cpp:1562
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<p>The project file \"%1\" was created by a previous version of Kile.<br/>It "
"needs to be updated before it can be opened.</p><p>Do you want to update it?"
"</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>ໄຟລ໌ໂຄງການ \"%1\" ຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໂດຍ Kile ເວີຊັນເກົ່າ.<br/"
">ມັນຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງໄດ້ຮັບການອັບເດດກ່ອນທີ່ຈະເປີດໄດ້.</p><p>ທ່ານຕ້ອງການອັບເດດມັນຫຼືບໍ່?"
"</p>"

#: kiledocmanager.cpp:1565
#, kde-format
msgid "Project File Needs to be Updated"
msgstr "ໄຟລ໌ໂຄງການຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງໄດ້ຮັບການອັບເດດ"

#: kiledocmanager.cpp:1572
#, kde-format
