"the first page."
msgstr ""
"ຄຳສັ່ງນີ້ສ້າງຫົວຂໍ້ໃນໜ້າຫົວຂໍ້ແຍກຕ່າງຫາກ\n"
"- ຍົກເວັ້ນໃນປະເພດບົດຄວາມ (article), "
"ເຊິ່ງຫົວຂໍ້ຈະຢູ່ທາງເທິງຂອງໜ້າທຳອິດໂດຍປົກກະຕິ."

#: kilestdactions.cpp:53
#, kde-format
msgid "Table of Contents - \\tableofcontents"
msgstr "ສາລະບານ - \\tableofcontents"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:56
#, kde-format
msgid "Put this command where you want the table of contents to go"
msgstr "ໃສ່ຄຳສັ່ງນີ້ບ່ອນທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການໃຫ້ສາລະບານສະແດງ"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:57
#, kde-format
msgid "Title Definition - \\title{}"
msgstr "ການກຳນົດຫົວຂໍ້ - \\title{}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:57
#, kde-format
msgid "Title Definition"
msgstr "ການກຳນົດຫົວຂໍ້"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:60
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"\\title{text}\n"
"The \\title command declares text to be the title.\n"
"Use \\\\ to tell LaTeX where to start a new line in a long title."
msgstr ""
"\\title{text}\n"
"ຄຳສັ່ງ \\title ປະກາດຂໍ້ຄວາມໃຫ້ເປັນຫົວຂໍ້.\n"
"ໃຊ້ \\\\ ເພື່ອບອກ LaTeX ບ່ອນທີ່ຈະເລີ່ມແຖວໃໝ່ໃນຫົວຂໍ້ທີ່ຍາວ."

#: kilestdactions.cpp:61
#, kde-format
msgid "Author Definition - \\author{}"
msgstr "ການກຳນົດຜູ້ຂຽນ - \\author{}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:61
#, kde-format
msgid "Author Definition"
msgstr "ການກຳນົດຜູ້ຂຽນ"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:64
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"\\author{names}\n"
"The \\author command declares the author(s), where names is a list of "
"authors separated by \\and commands."
msgstr ""
"\\author{names}\n"
"ຄຳສັ່ງ \\author ປະກາດຜູ້ຂຽນ, ເຊິ່ງ names ແມ່ນລາຍການຂອງຜູ້ຂຽນທີ່ແຍກດ້ວຍຄຳສັ່ງ "
"\\and."

#: kilestdactions.cpp:66
#, kde-format
msgid "Center - \\begin{center}"
msgstr "ຈັດກາງ - \\begin{center}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:69 kilestdactions.cpp:73 kilestdactions.cpp:77
#, kde-format
msgid "Each line must be terminated with the string \\\\."
msgstr "ແຕ່ລະແຖວຕ້ອງສິ້ນສຸດດ້ວຍ \\\\."

#: kilestdactions.cpp:70
#, kde-format
msgid "Align Left - \\begin{flushleft}"
msgstr "ຈັດຊິດຊ້າຍ - \\begin{flushleft}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:74
#, kde-format
msgid "Align Right - \\begin{flushright}"
msgstr "ຈັດຊິດຂວາ - \\begin{flushright}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:78
#, kde-format
msgid "Quote - \\begin{quote}"
msgstr "ຄຳອ້າງອີງສັ້ນ - \\begin{quote}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:78
#, kde-format
msgid "Quote"
msgstr "ຄຳອ້າງອີງສັ້ນ"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:81
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The text is justified at both margins.\n"
"Leaving a blank line between text produces a new paragraph."
msgstr ""
"ຂໍ້ຄວາມຖືກຈັດໃຫ້ສະເໝີກັນທັງສອງຂອບ.\n"
"ການປະແຖວຫວ່າງລະຫວ່າງຂໍ້ຄວາມຈະສ້າງວັກໃໝ່."

#: kilestdactions.cpp:82
#, kde-format
msgid "Quotation - \\begin{quotation}"
msgstr "ຄຳອ້າງອີງຍາວ - \\begin{quotation}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:82
#, kde-format
msgid "Quotation"
msgstr "ຄຳອ້າງອີງຍາວ"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:85
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The text is justified at both margins and there is paragraph indentation.\n"
"Leaving a blank line between text produces a new paragraph."
msgstr ""
"ຂໍ້ຄວາມຖືກຈັດໃຫ້ສະເໝີກັນທັງສອງຂອບ ແລະ ມີການຫຍໍ້ໜ້າວັກ.\n"
"ການປະແຖວຫວ່າງລະຫວ່າງຂໍ້ຄວາມຈະສ້າງວັກໃໝ່."

#: kilestdactions.cpp:86
#, kde-format
msgid "Verse - \\begin{verse}"
msgstr "ບົດກອນ - \\begin{verse}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:86
#, kde-format
msgid "Verse"
msgstr "ບົດກອນ"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:89
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The verse environment is designed for poetry.\n"
"Separate the lines of each stanza with \\\\, and use one or more blank lines "
"to separate the stanzas."
msgstr ""
"ສະພາບແວດລ້ອມ verse ຖືກອອກແບບມາສຳລັບບົດກອນ.\n"
"ແຍກແຖວຂອງແຕ່ລະວັກດ້ວຍ \\\\, ແລະ ໃຊ້ແຖວຫວ່າງໜຶ່ງ ຫຼື "
"ຫຼາຍກວ່າເພື່ອແຍກແຕ່ລະວັກ."

#: kilestdactions.cpp:91
#, kde-format
msgid "Verbatim - \\begin{verbatim}"
msgstr "ຂໍ້ຄວາມຕາມຕົ້ນສະບັບ - \\begin{verbatim}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:94
#, kde-format
msgid "Environment that gets LaTeX to print exactly what you type in."
msgstr "ສະພາບແວດລ້ອມທີ່ໃຫ້ LaTeX ພິມສິ່ງທີ່ທ່ານພິມລົງໄປແປະໆ."

#: kilestdactions.cpp:95
#, kde-format
msgid "Bulleted List - \\begin{itemize}"
msgstr "ລາຍການຈຸດ - \\begin{itemize}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:95
#, kde-format
msgid "Bulleted List"
msgstr "ລາຍການຈຸດ"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:98
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The itemize environment produces a 'bulleted' list.\n"
"Each item of an itemized list begins with an \\item command."
msgstr ""
"ສະພາບແວດລ້ອມ itemize ສ້າງລາຍການທີ່ມີ 'ຈຸດ'.\n"
"ແຕ່ລະລາຍການເລີ່ມຕົ້ນດ້ວຍຄຳສັ່ງ \\item."

#: kilestdactions.cpp:99
#, kde-format
msgid "Enumeration - \\begin{enumerate}"
msgstr "ລາຍການຕົວເລກ - \\begin{enumerate}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:99
#, kde-format
msgid "Enumeration"
msgstr "ລາຍການຕົວເລກ"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:102
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The enumerate environment produces a numbered list.\n"
"Each item of an enumerated list begins with an \\item command."
msgstr ""
"ສະພາບແວດລ້ອມ enumerate ສ້າງລາຍການທີ່ມີຕົວເລກ.\n"
"ແຕ່ລະລາຍການເລີ່ມຕົ້ນດ້ວຍຄຳສັ່ງ \\item."

#: kilestdactions.cpp:103
#, kde-format
msgid "Description - \\begin{description}"
msgstr "ລາຍການຄຳອະທິບາຍ - \\begin{description}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:106
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The description environment is used to make labeled lists.\n"
"Each item of the list begins with an \\item[label] command.\n"
"The 'label' is bold face and flushed right."
msgstr ""
"ສະພາບແວດລ້ອມ description ໃຊ້ເພື່ອສ້າງລາຍການທີ່ມີປ້າຍຊື່.\n"
"ແຕ່ລະລາຍການເລີ່ມຕົ້ນດ້ວຍຄຳສັ່ງ \\item[label].\n"
"'label' ແມ່ນໂຕໜາ ແລະ ຊິດຂວາ."

#: kilestdactions.cpp:108
#, kde-format
msgid "Table - \\begin{table}"
msgstr "ຕາຕະລາງ - \\begin{table}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:111
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"\\begin{table}[placement]\n"
"body of the table\n"
"\\caption{table title}\n"
"\\end{table}\n"
"Tables are objects that are not part of the normal text, and are usually "
"floated to a convenient place.\n"
"The optional argument [placement] determines where LaTeX will try to place "
"your table\n"
"h : Here - at the position in the text where the table environment appears\n"
"t : Top - at the top of a text page\n"
"b : Bottom - at the bottom of a text page\n"
"p : Page of floats - on a separate float page, which is a page containing no "
"text, only floats.\n"
"The body of the table is made up of whatever text or LaTeX commands, etc., "
"you wish.\n"
"The \\caption command allows you to title your table."
msgstr ""
"\\begin{table}[placement]\n"
"body of the table\n"
"\\caption{table title}\n"
"\\end{table}\n"
"ຕາຕະລາງແມ່ນວັດຖຸທີ່ບໍ່ແມ່ນສ່ວນໜຶ່ງຂອງຂໍ້ຄວາມປົກກະຕິ, ແລະ ມັກຈະຖືກ float "
"ໄປບ່ອນທີ່ເໝາະສົມ.\n"
"argument ທາງເລືອກ [placement] ກຳນົດບ່ອນທີ່ LaTeX ຈະພະຍາຍາມວາງຕາຕະລາງຂອງທ່ານ\n"
"h : Here - ທີ່ຕຳແໜ່ງໃນຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ສະພາບແວດລ້ອມຕາຕະລາງປາກົດ\n"
"t : Top - ຢູ່ທາງເທິງຂອງໜ້າຂໍ້ຄວາມ\n"
"b : Bottom - ຢູ່ທາງລຸ່ມຂອງໜ້າຂໍ້ຄວາມ\n"
"p : Page of floats - ໃນໜ້າ float ແຍກຕ່າງຫາກ, ເຊິ່ງເປັນໜ້າທີ່ບໍ່ມີຂໍ້ຄວາມ, "
"ມີແຕ່ floats.\n"
"ເນື້ອຫາຂອງຕາຕະລາງປະກອບດ້ວຍຂໍ້ຄວາມ ຫຼື ຄຳສັ່ງ LaTeX ຕ່າງໆທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການ.\n"
"ຄຳສັ່ງ \\caption ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານໃສ່ຫົວຂໍ້ຕາຕະລາງໄດ້."

#: kilestdactions.cpp:115
#, kde-format
msgid "Figure - \\begin{figure}"
msgstr "ຮູບ - \\begin{figure}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:118
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"\\begin{figure}[placement]\n"
"body of the figure\n"
"\\caption{figure title}\n"
"\\end{figure}\n"
"Figures are objects that are not part of the normal text, and are usually "
"floated to a convenient place.\n"
"The optional argument [placement] determines where LaTeX will try to place "
"your figure\n"
"h : Here - at the position in the text where the figure environment appears\n"
"t : Top - at the top of a text page\n"
"b : Bottom - at the bottom of a text page\n"
"p : Page of floats - on a separate float page, which is a page containing no "
"text, only floats.\n"
"The body of the figure is made up of whatever text or LaTeX commands, etc., "
"you wish.\n"
"The \\caption command allows you to title your figure."
msgstr ""
"\\begin{figure}[placement]\n"
"body of the figure\n"
"\\caption{figure title}\n"
"\\end{figure}\n"
"ຮູບແມ່ນວັດຖຸທີ່ບໍ່ແມ່ນສ່ວນໜຶ່ງຂອງຂໍ້ຄວາມປົກກະຕິ, ແລະ ມັກຈະຖືກ float "
"ໄປບ່ອນທີ່ເໝາະສົມ.\n"
"argument ທາງເລືອກ [placement] ກຳນົດບ່ອນທີ່ LaTeX ຈະພະຍາຍາມວາງຮູບຂອງທ່ານ\n"
"h : Here - ທີ່ຕຳແໜ່ງໃນຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ສະພາບແວດລ້ອມຮູບປາກົດ\n"
"t : Top - ຢູ່ທາງເທິງຂອງໜ້າຂໍ້ຄວາມ\n"
"b : Bottom - ຢູ່ທາງລຸ່ມຂອງໜ້າຂໍ້ຄວາມ\n"
"p : Page of floats - ໃນໜ້າ float ແຍກຕ່າງຫາກ, ເຊິ່ງເປັນໜ້າທີ່ບໍ່ມີຂໍ້ຄວາມ, "
"ມີແຕ່ floats.\n"
"ເນື້ອຫາຂອງຮູບປະກອບດ້ວຍຂໍ້ຄວາມ ຫຼື ຄຳສັ່ງ LaTeX ຕ່າງໆທີ່ທ່ານຕ້ອງການ.\n"
"ຄຳສັ່ງ \\caption ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານໃສ່ຫົວຂໍ້ຮູບໄດ້."

#: kilestdactions.cpp:122
#, kde-format
msgid "Title Page - \\begin{titlepage}"
msgstr "ໜ້າຫົວຂໍ້ - \\begin{titlepage}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:122
#, kde-format
msgid "Title Page"
msgstr "ໜ້າຫົວຂໍ້"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:125
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"\\begin{titlepage}\n"
"text\n"
"\\end{titlepage}\n"
"The titlepage environment creates a title page, i.e. a page with no printed "
"page number or heading."
msgstr ""
"\\begin{titlepage}\n"
"text\n"
"\\end{titlepage}\n"
"ສະພາບແວດລ້ອມ titlepage ສ້າງໜ້າຫົວຂໍ້, ເຊັ່ນ: "
"ໜ້າທີ່ບໍ່ມີເລກໜ້າຫຼືຫົວຂໍ້ພິມຢູ່."

#: kilestdactions.cpp:127
#, kde-format
msgid "Italics - \\textit{}"
msgstr "ໂຕອຽງ - \\textit{}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:127
#, kde-format
msgid "Italics"
msgstr "ໂຕອຽງ"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:129
#, kde-format
msgid "\\textit{italic text}"
msgstr "\\textit{italic text}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:130
#, kde-format
msgid "Slanted - \\textsl{}"
msgstr "ໂຕອຽງ (Slanted) - \\textsl{}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:130 kilestdactions.cpp:449
#, kde-format
msgid "Slanted"
msgstr "ໂຕອຽງ (Slanted)"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:133
#, kde-format
msgid "\\textsl{slanted text}"
msgstr "\\textsl{slanted text}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:134
#, kde-format
msgid "Boldface - \\textbf{}"
msgstr "ໂຕໜາ - \\textbf{}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:134
#, kde-format
msgid "Boldface"
msgstr "ໂຕໜາ"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:137
#, kde-format
msgid "\\textbf{boldface text}"
msgstr "\\textbf{boldface text}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:138
#, kde-format
msgid "Typewriter - \\texttt{}"
msgstr "ພິມດີດ - \\texttt{}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:138
#, kde-format
msgid "Typewriter"
msgstr "ພິມດີດ"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:141
#, kde-format
msgid "\\texttt{typewriter text}"
msgstr "\\texttt{typewriter text}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:142
#, kde-format
msgid "Small Caps - \\textsc{}"
msgstr "ໂຕພິມໃຫຍ່ຂະໜາດນ້ອຍ - \\textsc{}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:142
#, kde-format
msgid "Small Caps"
msgstr "ໂຕພິມໃຫຍ່ຂະໜາດນ້ອຍ"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:145
#, kde-format
msgid "\\textsc{small caps text}"
msgstr "\\textsc{small caps text}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:149
#, kde-format
msgid "\\item[label] Hello!"
msgstr "\\item[label] ສະບາຍດີ!"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:151
#, kde-format
msgid "Tabbing - \\begin{tabbing}"
msgstr "Tabbing - \\begin{tabbing}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:154
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The tabbing environment provides a way to align text in columns.\n"
"\\begin{tabbing}\n"
"text \\= more text \\= still more text \\= last text \\\\\n"
"second row \\&gt;  \\&gt; more \\\\\n"
"\\end{tabbing}\n"
"Commands :\n"
"\\=  Sets a tab stop at the current position.\n"
"\\>  Advances to the next tab stop.\n"
"\\&lt;  Allows you to put something to the left of the local margin without "
"changing the margin. Can only be used at the start of the line.\n"
"\\+  Moves the left margin of the next and all the following commands one "
"tab stop to the right\n"
"\\-  Moves the left margin of the next and all the following commands one "
"tab stop to the left\n"
"\\' Moves everything that you have typed so far in the current column to the "
"right of the previous column, flush against the current column's tab stop. \n"
"\\`  Allows you to put text flush right against any tab stop, including tab "
"stop 0\n"
"\\kill  Sets tab stops without producing text.\n"
"\\a  In a tabbing environment, the commands \\=, \\' and \\` do not produce "
"accents as normal. Instead, the commands \\a=, \\a' and \\a` are used."
msgstr ""
"ສະພາບແວດລ້ອມ tabbing ໃຫ້ວິທີການຈັດຂໍ້ຄວາມໃນຖັນ.\n"
"\\begin{tabbing}\n"
"text \\= more text \\= still more text \\= last text \\\\\n"
"second row \\&gt;  \\&gt; more \\\\\n"
"\\end{tabbing}\n"
"Commands :\n"
"\\=  ຕັ້ງຄ່າ tab stop ທີ່ຕຳແໜ່ງປັດຈຸບັນ.\n"
"\\>  ຂ້າມໄປຍັງ tab stop ຖັດໄປ.\n"
"\\&lt;  ອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ທ່ານໃສ່ບາງຢ່າງທາງຊ້າຍຂອງຂອບໂດຍບໍ່ປ່ຽນຂອບ. "
"ໃຊ້ໄດ້ສະເພາະຕອນເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແຖວ.\n"
"\\+  ຍ້າຍຂອບຊ້າຍຂອງຄຳສັ່ງຖັດໄປ ແລະ ທັງໝົດຕາມຫຼັງໄປທາງຂວາໜຶ່ງ tab stop\n"
"\\-  ຍ້າຍຂອບຊ້າຍຂອງຄຳສັ່ງຖັດໄປ ແລະ ທັງໝົດຕາມຫຼັງໄປທາງຊ້າຍໜຶ່ງ tab stop\n"
"\\' ຍ້າຍທຸກຢ່າງທີ່ທ່ານພິມມາໃນຖັນປັດຈຸບັນໄປທາງຂວາຂອງຖັນກ່ອນໜ້າ, "
"ຊິດກັບ tab stop ຂອງຖັນປັດຈຸບັນ. \n"
"\\`  ອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ທ່ານໃສ່ຂໍ້ຄວາມຊິດຂວາກັບ tab stop ໃດກໍໄດ້, ລວມທັງ tab "
"stop 0\n"
"\\kill  ຕັ້ງຄ່າ tab stops ໂດຍບໍ່ສ້າງຂໍ້ຄວາມ.\n"
"\\a  ໃນສະພາບແວດລ້ອມ tabbing, ຄຳສັ່ງ \\=, \\' ແລະ \\` ບໍ່ສ້າງ "
"accents ຕາມປົກກະຕິ. ແທນທີ່ຈະເປັນແນວນັ້ນ, ຄຳສັ່ງ \\a=, \\a' ແລະ \\a` "
"ຖືກນຳໃຊ້."

#: kilestdactions.cpp:155
#, kde-format
msgid "Tabular - \\begin{tabular}"
msgstr "ຕາຕະລາງ - \\begin{tabular}"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:158
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"\\begin{tabular}[pos]{cols}\n"
"column 1 entry & column 2 entry ... & column n entry \\\\\n"
"...\n"
"\\end{tabular}\n"
"pos : Specifies the vertical position; default is alignment on the center of "
"the environment.\n"
"     t - align on top row\n"
"     b - align on bottom row\n"
"cols : Specifies the column formatting.\n"
"     l - A column of left-aligned items.\n"
"     r - A column of right-aligned items.\n"
"     c - A column of centered items.\n"
"     | - A vertical line the full height and depth of the environment.\n"
"     @{text} - this inserts text in every row.\n"
"The \\hline command draws a horizontal line the width of the table.\n"
"The \\cline{i-j} command draws horizontal lines across the columns "
"specified, beginning in column i and ending in column j.\n"
"The \\vline command draws a vertical line extending the full height and "
"depth of its row."
msgstr ""
"\\begin{tabular}[pos]{cols}\n"
"column 1 entry & column 2 entry ... & column n entry \\\\\n"
"...\n"
"\\end{tabular}\n"
"pos : ລະບຸຕຳແໜ່ງລວງຕັ້ງ; ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນຈັດກາງຂອງສະພາບແວດລ້ອມ.\n"
"     t - ຈັດໃຫ້ສະເໝີກັບແຖວເທິງສຸດ\n"
"     b - ຈັດໃຫ້ສະເໝີກັບແຖວລຸ່ມສຸດ\n"
"cols : ລະບຸຮູບແບບຖັນ.\n"
"     l - ຖັນຂອງລາຍການຊິດຊ້າຍ.\n"
"     r - ຖັນຂອງລາຍການຊິດຂວາ.\n"
"     c - ຖັນຂອງລາຍການຈັດກາງ.\n"
"     | - ເສັ້ນຕັ້ງເຕັມຄວາມສູງ ແລະ ເລິກຂອງສະພາບແວດລ້ອມ.\n"
"     @{text} - ອັນນີ້ແຊກຂໍ້ຄວາມໃນທຸກແຖວ.\n"
"ຄຳສັ່ງ \\hline ແຕ້ມເສັ້ນນອນຕາມຄວາມກວ້າງຂອງຕາຕະລາງ.\n"
"ຄຳສັ່ງ \\cline{i-j} ແຕ້ມເສັ້ນນອນຂ້າມຖັນທີ່ລະບຸ, ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນໃນຖັນ i ແລະ ສິ້ນສຸດໃນຖັນ "
"j.\n"
"ຄຳສັ່ງ \\vline ແຕ້ມເສັ້ນຕັ້ງເຕັມຄວາມສູງ ແລະ ເລິກຂອງແຖວມັນ."

#: kilestdactions.cpp:159
#, kde-format
msgid "Multicolumn Cells - \\multicolumn"
msgstr "ເຊວຫຼາຍຖັນ - \\multicolumn"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:159
#, kde-format
msgid "Multicolumn Cells"
msgstr "ເຊວຫຼາຍຖັນ"

#: kilestdactions.cpp:162
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"\\multicolumn{cols}{pos}{text}\n"
"col, specifies the number of columns to span.\n"
"pos specifies the formatting of the entry: c for centered, l for flushleft, "
"r for flushright.\n"
"text specifies what text is to make up the entry."
msgstr ""
"\\multicolumn{cols}{pos}{text}\n"
"col, ລະບຸຈຳນວນຖັນທີ່ຈະກວມເອົາ.\n"
"pos ລະບຸຮູບແບບຂອງລາຍການ: c ສຳລັບຈັດກາງ, l ສຳລັບຊິດຊ້າຍ, r ສຳລັບຊິດຂວາ.\n"
"text ລະບຸຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ຈະໃສ່ໃນລາຍການ."

